  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Alex is on half board. </p>
<p>Each day enjoy an excellent breakfast buffet with a range of hot and cold options.</p>
<p>Four or five course evening meals are served each day, with a choice of main course - meals are prepared using seasonal ingredients, with a menu inspired by local flavours. There is also a weekly gala dinner.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners included</p>]]></cateringDescription>
