  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic North Facing Bedrooms </strong>are around 22-26<span>m² and sleep two people, with North facing views. South Facing Bedrooms are on request, please give our Reservations team a call to book a South facing bedroom.</span></p>
<p><strong>Deluxe North Facing Bedrooms</strong> are around 31<span>m² sleeping two people.  These bedrooms have a double bed, seating area and balcony with North facing views.  </span>South Facing Bedrooms are on request, please give our Reservations team a call to book a South facing bedroom.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> offer the most space at around 40<span>m². These north facing rooms can sleep up to three (additional single bed or sofa bed) and have a balcony and fireplace.</span></p>
<p><strong>Small single</strong> rooms are around 15-21m<span>², sleeping one person.</span></p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Bedroom facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Bathrobes</li>
<li>Desk</li>
<li>Bathroom with bath or shower</li>
<li>Cots are available at a cost of 25 CHF per day </li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></roomsDescription>
